    //   2. nv_consume_enter_shield(1) installs shield с 1ms deadline.
    //   3. on_exit Time.sleep(50) suspend → nv_shield_check_deadline fires.
    //   4. _nova_throw_cleanup_timeout_fn invoked (codegen-emitted typed impl).
    //   5. NOVA_TID_USER_CleanupTimeoutError macro defined в TU.
